  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Hilton Bujumbura</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The Project will: (i) address the supply-demand gap for business hotels of international standards, providing key business infrastructure as the Country emerges from a post-conflict status; and (ii) raise  the country hotel standards by supporting the establishment of a 4-star internationally managed hotel in the country.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The proposed project consists of the renovation and rebranding of the former 3-star 106 keys Novotel hotel in Bujumbura, Burundi into a 4-star 138-room Doubletree by Hilton hotel (the Projector the hotelor Hilton Bujumbura). The hotel will be the first international, upscale brand operating in Burundi and will address the lack of adequate accommodation facilities in Bujumbura.</narrative>
  </description>
